short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Modify YouTube thumbnails to be Rick Astley's Never Gonna Give You Up

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A fork of a project by github.com/MagicJinn/MrBeastify-Youtube, this extension changes all YouTube thumbnails to the thumbnail for Never Gonna Give You Up by Rick Astley.
